commit_message:
openstackcloud: properly handle scheduler_hints

Scheduler hints need to be specified at the top level of the JSON being
submitted to the API, i.e.

```
{
  "server": {...},
  "os:scheduler_hints": {...}
}
```

instead of

```
{
  "server": {
    "os:scheduler_hints": {...}
  }
}
```

Change-Id: I19b5736b87e4b323bb957bd247b45e87bf3e8227
Task: 22955

